<h3 class="mb-4">Send Game Mail</h3>

<div class="card bg-dark border-secondary">
  <div class="card-body">
    <form method="POST" action="/admin/gamemail">
      <input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="<%= csrfToken %>">
      <div class="mb-3">
        <label class="form-label text-muted">Character Name</label>
        <input type="text" name="character" class="form-control bg-dark text-light border-secondary" placeholder="Character name" required>
      </div>
      <div class="mb-3">
        <label class="form-label text-muted">Subject</label>
        <input type="text" name="subject" class="form-control bg-dark text-light border-secondary" placeholder="Mail subject" required>
      </div>
      <div class="mb-3">
        <label class="form-label text-muted">Message</label>
        <textarea name="message" class="form-control bg-dark text-light border-secondary" rows="5" placeholder="Mail body" required></textarea>
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-gold"><i class="fas fa-paper-plane me-1"></i>Send Mail</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="card bg-dark border-secondary mt-4">
  <div class="card-header text-gold">Note</div>
  <div class="card-body text-muted">
    <p class="mb-0">Game mail is sent via SOAP. Ensure your SOAP credentials are configured in the <code>.env</code> file (SOAP_HOST, SOAP_PORT, SOAP_USER, SOAP_PASS). The character must exist in the game database.</p>
  </div>
</div>
